## Worked Example: Merged Steps on One File

> **Principle:** Don't skip verification — skip the intermediate file state. When two plan steps touch the same file, run READ for both together, PROPOSE a single merged diff, TEST once, then VERIFY each step's claims against the SAME final file. Mark both SHIPPED in one turn only after BOTH VERIFY tables are all ✅.

### Phase A — READ (both steps, pre-state together)

```
rg '<DataReviewAssistantPanel'  → 1 match  (L1014)
rg 'Cp1MobileAssistantSheet'    → 0 matches (not yet created)
```

**Findings:**
- `postComputeCtx` exists at L638–641 but not threaded through `buildPostComputeOpeningMessage`
- `<DataReviewAssistantPanel>` duplicated at L1014–1025 (same component, two sites)
- No `Cp1MobileAssistantSheet` import or mount anywhere

### Phase B — PROPOSE (single merged diff)

| Change | Files | Detail |
|--------|-------|--------|
| Refactor L638–641 | `DataReviewRoute.tsx` | Pass `postComputeCtx` + `assistantVisible` into return tree |
| Add `isDesktop` + `resultsAssistantProps` | `DataReviewRoute.tsx` | Desktop panel: pass props to `<DataReviewAssistantPanel>` |
| DELETE L1014–1025 | `DataReviewRoute.tsx` | Remove duplicate `<DataReviewAssistantPanel>` mount |
| INSERT mobile sheet | `DataReviewRoute.tsx` | `<Cp1MobileAssistantSheet>` mirroring `DataUploadRoute` L687–695 |

### Phase C — TEST (one implementation pass)

Single edit: `DataReviewRoute.tsx` — delete duplicate, add `isDesktop` conditional, insert `<Cp1MobileAssistantSheet>`.

### Phase D — VERIFY Step 1 table

| Claim | Command / Read | Pass when | Pass |
|-------|---------------|-----------|:----:|
| `postComputeCtx` threaded | `rg 'postComputeCtx' DataReviewRoute.tsx` | ≥2 uses, 1 declaration | ✅ |
| `buildPostComputeContext` called | `rg 'buildPostComputeContext\(' DataReviewRoute.tsx` | exactly 1 call | ✅ |
| `buildPostComputeOpeningMessage` receives ctx | `rg 'buildPostComputeOpeningMessage\(postComputeCtx' DataReviewRoute.tsx` | ≥1 | ✅ |

### Phase D — VERIFY Step 2 table

| Claim | Command / Read | Pass when | Pass |
|-------|---------------|-----------|:----:|
| `<DataReviewAssistantPanel>` single mount | `rg '<DataReviewAssistantPanel' DataReviewRoute.tsx` | exactly 1 direct mount | ✅ |
| `Cp1MobileAssistantSheet` imported + mounted | `rg 'Cp1MobileAssistantSheet' DataReviewRoute.tsx` | import + mount | ✅ |
| `isDesktop` conditional gating | `rg 'isDesktop' DataReviewRoute.tsx` | ≥2 conditionals | ✅ |
| `variant="mobile-sheet"` gone | `rg 'variant.*mobile-sheet' DataReviewRoute.tsx` | 0 matches | ✅ |

### Phase E — Checkpoint

```
## Checkpoint — Phase N
| Step | READ | PROPOSE | TEST | VERIFY | Status |
|------|:----:|:-------:|:----:|:------:|:--------|
| N.1 | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | SHIPPED |
| N.2 | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | SHIPPED |
```

Both steps SHIPPED in one turn — evidence per claim per step, zero intermediate commits.

