## Checkpoint table (after every step)

```markdown
## Checkpoint — Phase N
| Step | READ | PROPOSE | TEST | VERIFY | Status |
|------|:----:|:-------:|:----:|:------:|:--------|
| N.1 | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | SHIPPED |
| N.2 | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | IN PROGRESS — … |
| N.3 | — | — | — | — | NOT STARTED |
```

**Forbidden until checkpoint shows all steps SHIPPED:**
- “Phase complete”
- “All tests green” (without per-step evidence)
- “Ready for next phase”

