## Anti-patterns

| Anti-pattern | VERIFY catch |
|--------------|--------------|
| Status ✅ from conversation memory | `rg` / `Glob` in **this** session |
| “17 vitest + 6 sbt” but spec file missing | `Glob **/*Spec*` for named spec |
| Consolidation step without new module | `Glob **/module-name.ts` |
| Docs "done" with stale gate rows | Read full gate block in `agent_schema.md` |
| Skip to next phase with open VERIFY ❌ | Checkpoint blocks advance |
| **“Hook + mount = mobile done”** | Plan splits UX from logic — verify BOTH exist: `rg 'variant.*mobile-sheet'` AND `rg 'export function MobileFAB'` |
| **Multi-plan merge mixes done bars** | Each plan has its own checkpoint; never collapse 053 security + 052-B perf into one ✅ |
| **Checkpoint labels diverge across runs** | Lock column names: step N.n uses the plan's own step ID, not "hook" vs "mobile UX" |
| **Optional step labeled done** | If plan says "optional: chat-access.ts", verify it was marked SKIPPED, not silently omitted and claimed done |
| **scrollToEntity discussed but unverified** | Thread discussions are not VERIFY rows — if it's in the plan, it needs a grep/Read row |
| **Tracks only files, not wiring** | `rg` the route/handler/adapter registration — a file existing ≠ it being wired |
| **Implementation diverges from plan silently** | Diff the plan's §Implementation list against actual files touched; if they don't match, amendment gate triggered |

